  "headline": "Decode-path scatter+LP avoidance removes ~112 us/step (tree M=32, scatter+LP); net 87-112 us/step (conservative-realistic) = 0.86-1.11% of the step at the clear-500 bar (E[T]=4.862); lowers the bar to 4.808-4.820 and adds a ~flat +4.3 to +5.6 TPS at any E[T]. Greedy-safe (PPL untouched), NON-drafter, STACKS with the descent. Second-order but real denominator insurance on the fern #145 >=90%-spread-recovery risk.",
  "scope": "LOCAL A10G profiling + analysis. No HF Job / no submission / no served-file change. BASELINE stays 481.53 (PPL 2.3777). Bounds a greedy-safe NON-drafter step_time (denominator) lever + hands a build design; does NOT authorize a launch.",
